name: Doggystyle PoV - Realistic
description:
This model was trained using pictures from Google Images and PornPics.com. The base model used for trainning was QGO-10a.


Every picture had the following words: a woman getting fucked by a man, doggystyle

Without these ones, the LoRa will probably not work. Further, there's a more extensive list, used to describe the picture.

Extensive list of trigger words:

  • What's the woman's skin colour?: white woman, latina woman

  • What's the man's skin colour?: white man, black man, latino man

  • Do they have tattoos?: man with tattoos, woman with tattoos

  • What are their arms doing?: man holding her ass, woman holding her ass, man holding her arms, man fingering her ass, woman fingering her ass

  • What's the woman's facial expression?: pain, moaning, smiling, neutral expression

  • Where are they having sex?: on a bed, on a couch, on the floor, on a desk, on a chair, in the shower

  • Which type of sex?: vaginal sex, anal sex

  • Where is the woman looking at?: looking to the side, looking at view

  • Does the woman have clothes?: naked, clothes

Some other words were used during training to describe the woman's clothing. Such as garnet, panties, shirt,... Feel free to describe the pieces of clothing, but it is not recommended.

Please, show me your renders so we can analyse them together and learn from inputs/prompts.

This model was made for pure entertainment.
When you use this model, the responsability on what you use the model for is fully yours.
